HUGA OPTOTECH IN said unconsolidated sales
in April fell 46.89% to NT$195,534,000 from NT$368,152,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2012           4/2011
Sales            195,534          368,152    
YOY%             -46.89%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            624,330         1,175,293   
YOY%             -46.88% 
=================================================================
 